divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting on the balcony at the Buena vista palace on the 20th floor looking south over downtown Disney in Kissimmee FL. It was dusk and from the horizon I noticed a group of lights ascending heading north west. No sound or discernible visual indication, except that I counted 14 of them in a mass group. At first it looked like a squadron of fighters taking off, but did not follow normal operational procedures. The spacing was varied and as they broke in distance from one another they slowly dissappeared in a westerly direction.
Summary: Strange lights over the horizon heading ne from south of Downtown Disney
